# React / Next.js Patterns

- Functional components only. No class components.
- Use `React.ReactNode` for children props, `React.ReactElement` when element-specific typing is needed.
- Use `next/image` for optimized images. Use `next/link` for internal navigation.
- All pages are static (no `params`, no `getServerSideProps`). Export metadata from page files for SEO.
- Layouts in `layout.tsx` handle shared chrome; pages in `page.tsx` handle content.
